s.\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 746, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His legacy\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 701}, {\"ngram\": \"future generations\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our thoughts and prayers are with Team Samoa and all those affected by this profound loss.\\\"\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 786, \"end\": 791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0673101946577943e-18, \"text\": \"Samoa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our thoughts\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 759}, {\"ngram\": \"prayers\", \"from\": 764, \"to\": 771}, {\"ngram\": \"this profound loss\", \"from\": 818, \"to\": 836}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pauga Talalelei Pauga, the President of the Samoan Olympic Committee, expressed the deep impact of Fatupaito\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s death, stating, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cOur thoughts and those of the entire Samoan sporting community are with Lionel\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s family, his boxers, and friends.\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 1087, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 884, \"end\": 890, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\", \"score\": 0.9999999524152383, \"rank\": 4.7535581039309646e-08, \"text\": \"Samoan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\"}, {\"begin\": 1009, \"end\": 1015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\", \"score\": 0.9999999524152383, \"rank\": 4.7535581039309646e-08, \"text\": \"Samoan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pauga Talalelei Pauga\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 861}, {\"ngram\": \"the President\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 876}, {\"ngram\": \"the deep impact\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 935}, {\"ngram\": \"Fatupaito\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s death\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 958}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cOur thoughts\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 984}, {\"ngram\": \"Lionel\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s family\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1061}, {\"ngram\": \"his boxers\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1073}, {\"ngram\": \"friends\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1086}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He will be greatly missed.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d In a testament to his influence, Pauga and SASNOC Secretary General Maureen Tuimalealiifano gathered with the Samoan delegation for a briefing and a heartfelt team prayer, highlighting the emotional support extended to those closest to Fatupaito.\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1364, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1186, \"end\": 1209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maureen_Tuimalealiifano\", \"score\": 0.99999863793666, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maureen Tuimalealiifano\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maureen_Tuimalealiifano\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maureen_Tuimalealiifano\"}, {\"begin\": 1228, \"end\": 1234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\", \"score\": 0.9999999524152383, \"rank\": 4.7535581039309646e-08, \"text\": \"Samoan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"greatly missed.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1117}, {\"ngram\": \"a testament\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1132}, {\"ngram\": \"his influence\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1149}, {\"ngram\": \"Pauga\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1156}, {\"ngram\": \"a briefing\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1260}, {\"ngram\": \"a heartfelt team prayer\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1288}, {\"ngram\": \"the emotional support\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1324}, {\"ngram\": \"Fatupaito\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1363}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ato Plodzicki-Faoagali, Samoa\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s sole boxer at the Games and a heavyweight contender, paid tribute to Fatupaito on Facebook.\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1491, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ato Plodzicki-Faoagali\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1388}, {\"ngram\": \"sole boxer\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1410}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1423}, {\"ngram\": \"a heavyweight contender\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1451}, {\"ngram\": \"tribute\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1465}, {\"ngram\": \"Fatupaito\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1478}, {\"ngram\": \"Facebook\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1490}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He was a kind and generous coach, not only with his time and material things but also his knowledge,\\\" Plodzicki-Faoagali reflected.\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1624, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a kind and generous coach\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1525}, {\"ngram\": \"his time\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1549}, {\"ngram\": \"material\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1562}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1569}, {\"ngram\": \"his knowledge\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1592}, {\"ngram\": \"Plodzicki-Faoagali\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1613}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He recalled meeting Fatupaito when he was just 15, trialing for Samoa\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s youth team.\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1710, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fatupaito\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1654}, {\"ngram\": \"Samoa\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s youth team\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1709}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cYour dream was to attend an Olympics with me and Dad.\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1767, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1763, \"end\": 1766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Revenge\", \"score\": 0.8912074849999551, \"rank\": 0.12207316122381504, \"text\": \"Dad\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Revenge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Revenge\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cYour dream\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1724}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympics\", \"from\": 1739, \"to\": 1750}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve left too early; we haven\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t had our first fight at the Olympics like we planned!\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d he lamented, illustrating the coach\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s integral role in his journey.\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1935, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1780}, {\"ngram\": \"our first fight\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 1829}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 1845}, {\"ngram\": \"the coach\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s integral role\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1919}, {\"ngram\": \"his journey\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 1934}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Plodzicki-Faoagali, a two-time Pacific Games champion, is set to fight Belgium\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Victor Schelstraete on Sunday.\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 2050, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Plodzicki-Faoagali\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 1955}, {\"ngram\": \"a two-time Pacific Games champion\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 1990}, {\"ngram\": \"Belgium\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 2008, \"to\": 2019}, {\"ngram\": \"Victor Schelstraete\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2039}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2049}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With high hopes for victory, Plodzicki-Faoagali is a favorite in the 92kg class and carries the weight of his coach\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s dreams and expectations into the ring.\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2209, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"high hopes\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2066}, {\"ngram\": \"victory\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2078}, {\"ngram\": \"Plodzicki-Faoagali\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2098}, {\"ngram\": \"the 92kg class\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2130}, {\"ngram\": \"the weight\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2153}, {\"ngram\": \"his coach\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009